<title>WHEN I SURVEY THE WONDROUS CROSS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kross maktak chuh ka ngaihtuoh tieng,
 Lopina Lal Cha thihna chuh;
 Ka punna pen manna'n ka ngai,
 Ka chapona chuh ka ngainiem.

[V2]
 2. Pathien Krista thihna lo chuh,
 Lalpa bangmah dang suong puong ka;
 Mantaklo thil ei hip haw cheng,
 A thisan ah ka pie vek hi.

[V3]
 3. A lu, A khut, A keng enin!
 Lungkham hehpihna a luongkhawm;
 Ziebang chuh a umkhawm ngei em?
 Linglukhuk lopi hungsuok tawh.

[V4]
 4. Khawvel cheng hi keia hileh,
 Pie vek lengle tawm taluo'na;
 Tawbang Pathien lungsiet mak chuh!
 Thagau, hinna, bangkim A deih.</lyrics>
</song>